label.value: specimen was processed in accordance with the specified SOP

definition.value: An information content entity indicating whether the specimen was processed in accordance with the specified SOP.

label.value: comment from blood specimen processing

definition.value: A textual entity that states additional information about the blood specimen or donor that is deemed relevant for specimen processing.

label.value: presence of gross hemolysis of plasma observed

definition.value: An information content entity indicating whether the presence of gross hemolysis of plasma was observed.

label.value: cell pellet volume

definition.value: A scalar measurement datum that is the output of a volume measurement assay that has a cell pellet as evaluant.

label.value: cell pellet specimen barcode

definition.value: A specimen barcode that is associated with a cell pellet specimen.

label.value: time of completion of blood cell pellet processing

definition.value: A data item indicating the time when processing of a blood cell pellet specimen was completed.

label.value: time of blood cell pellet transfer to storage

definition.value: A data item indicating the time when the blood cell pellet specimen was transferred to storage.

label.value: name of person processing blood cell pellet specimen

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who performed processing of the blood cell pellet specimen.

label.value: date of specimen placement on dry ice for transport

definition.value: A data item indicating the calendar date when a specimen was placed on dry ice for transport.

label.value: time of specimen placement on dry ice for transport

definition.value: A data item indicating the time when a specimen was placed on dry ice for transport.

label.value: date of specimen freezing at -70 to -80 degrees C

definition.value: A data item indicating the calendar date when a specimen was stored at -75_ � 5_C.

label.value: date of specimen transport

definition.value: A data item indicating the calendar date when a specimen was transported to another institution.

label.value: time of specimen transport

definition.value: A data item indicating the time when a specimen was transported to another institution.

label.value: specimen transporting organization

definition.value: A role borne by an organization that is the provider of a specimen that is transported to another organization.

label.value: specimen receiving organization

definition.value: A role borne by an organization that is the recipient of a specimen that is transported from another organization.

label.value: name of person responsible for specimen transport

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who is responsible for the transport of a specimen to another organization.

label.value: name of IATA-trained person verifying specimen transport

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who verified the specimen transport was according to best practice, international standards, and industry regulations as trained by the IATA.

label.value: date of receiving specimen transport

definition.value: A data item indicating the calendar date when a specimen was received after transport from another institution.

label.value: time of receiving specimen transport

definition.value: A data item indicating the time when a specimen was received after transport from another institution.

label.value: temperature of specimen collection packet at time of receipt

definition.value: A scalar measurement datum that is the output of a temperature measurement assay performed on a collection packet when it is received with a specimen.

label.value: name of person receiving specimen shipment

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who received the specimen that was transported from another organization.

label.value: specimen shipment received in good condition

definition.value: An information content entity indicating that the physical condition of a specimen upon receipt after transport was good.

label.value: specimen shipment received in poor condition

definition.value: An information content entity indicating that the physical condition of a specimen upon receipt after transport was poor.

label.value: comment on specimen integrity after transport

definition.value: A textual entity that states information about the physical integrity or wholeness of the specimen that is deemed relevant for the specimen transport process.

label.value: date of specimen receipt for pathologist processing

definition.value: A data item indicating the calendar date when a specimen arrives in the gross pathology room for processing and review.

label.value: time of receipt for pathologist processing

definition.value: A data item indicating the time when a specimen arrives in the gross pathology room for processing and review.

label.value: name of quality control inspector of specimen

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who performed a quality control inspection of the specimen that is to be transported to another organization.

label.value: name of data entry person for tissue recovery form

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who performed the data entry process for filling in a tissue recovery case report form.

label.value: name of team leader for filling out tissue recovery form

definition.value: A personal name that designates the person who is the leader of the team responsible for entering the tissue recovery form data.

label.value: FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: A standard operating procedure for fixation of a tissue to the state where it is completely infiltrated with a suitable histological wax and can be embedded ready for section cutting on the microtome for a formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: equipment maintained as per manufacturer recommendations

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether equipment was maintained following the manufacturers recommendations.

label.value: comment on maintenance discrepancy from manufacturer recommendations

definition.value: A textual entity that states information about maintenance discrepancies from manufacturer recommendations.

label.value: FFPE clearing agent role

definition.value: A role borne by a chemical that is realized in the formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) processes to remove alcohol used for specimen dehydration, remove stains, and prepare a specimen for infiltration medium.

label.value: adherence of alcohol stage duration to FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether duration of the alcohol stage followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: FFPE alcohol stage duration

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of the alcohol stage in a formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: adherence of dehydration process duration to FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether duration of the dehydration process followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: FFPE dehydration process duration

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration of the dehydration process in the formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: adherence of dehydration process temperature to FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether temperature of the dehydration process followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: FFPE dehydration process temperature

definition.value: A scalar measurement datum that is the output of a temperature measurement assay performed on a specimen in alcohol during the dehydration process  in a formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: adherence of stage and replicate numbers to FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether the number of stages and replicates followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: number of FFPE stages/replicates

definition.value: A data item that indicates the number of stages and replicates in a FFPE process.

label.value: adherence of duration in clearing agent to FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether the duration in clearing agent followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: FFPE clearing agent duration

definition.value: A time measurement datum that is the result of measuring the duration in clearing agent in the formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: adherence of temperature of clearing agent to FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether the temperature of clearing agent followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: FFPE clearing agent temperature

definition.value: A scalar measurement datum that is the output of a temperature measurement assay performed on a specimen in clearing agent in a formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: adherence to paraffin impregnation method in FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether the paraffin impregnation method followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: FFPE paraffin impregnation method

definition.value: A protocol for the paraffin impregnation step of a formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: adherence of paraffin temperature to FFPE tissue processing SOP

definition.value: An information content entity that indicates whether the paraffin temperature followed that prescribed in the FFPE tissue processing SOP.

label.value: FFPE paraffin temperature

definition.value: A scalar measurement datum that is the output of a temperature measurement assay performed on paraffin in a formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.

label.value: comment on FFPE tissue processing

definition.value: A textual entity that states information relevant to tissue processing in a formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded (FFPE) process.
